Create monitoring template:

Enterprise >> monitoring >> monitoring template

Create >> 
target type : 
target type category 	: databases
Target type 			: instance

CONTINUE.

NAME  : MY_DB_TEMPLATE
DESC : .....

check make this default 

Go to metrics thresholds.

select only metrics with thresholds.(list will be reduced).
For small demo change the table psace threshold percentages and also change the frequency from 30 min to 15 min.


Enterprise >> monitoring >> monitoring template

Click on new template and say apply.

Template will only override metrics that are common to both template and target.

ADD:

select the targets.


finish

